content:
I am having this same issue with my Att.net account.

It was working fine until about 6pm Nov 11 and then all the sudden it stopped connecting.

Like you, I have YEARS of folders with information I cannot loose.

I have searched, googled, called AT&T 3 times in hopes that they can help. NO

I have searched this forum and found someone with a similar issue and I did EVERY SINGLE THING that the responder told that person to do. Everything on my side shows it is set up correctly but NOTHING is pulling in, yet I can get it on the yahoo.com site but all my other information is in TB.

I am hoping someone will answer your questions / issues and help us both.

Sorry for piggy backing on your post. I am hoping it will gab someones attention that we are both having the same issue and someone will be able to help.

YOU ARE NOT ALONE! though that doesn't fix either of our issues.
